The GPLv2 text is kept in:

  LICENSES/preferred/GPL-2.0

The syscall exception text is kept in:

  LICENSES/exceptions/Linux-syscall-note

Individual vendored or imported files may carry their own compatible SPDX
license identifiers. Those file-local notices remain authoritative for those
files.
